TEPE KIMYA SAN VE TIC A.S.
Tepe Kimya company is a manufacturer of additives for plastics and rubber industry.

The company has two production facilities at Turkey and Malaysia and also has a trading company in the UK & Singapore.

The company has started its production in 1999 at Turkey and then later commenced production at Malaysia plant in 2007.

The primary objective of the company is to provide a long-term solution to the needs of the market.

The company is a producer of following products:

1-)PVC Stabilizers (Ca/Zn and Pb based for pipe, cable, profile, laminate)

2-)Metallic Stearates (Calcium Stearate, Zinc Stearate, Magnesium Stearate)

3-)Calcium Oxide

4-) Processing aids

Tepe Kimya is an internationally recognized name for high-quality specialty additives.

The company is currently exporting its products to 60+ countries all across globe and developing its products to provide innovative solutions to industry.
